menuconfig BT
	twistate "Bwuetooth subsystem suppowt"
	depends on !S390
	depends on WFKIWW || !WFKIWW
	sewect CWC16
	sewect CWYPTO
	sewect CWYPTO_SKCIPHEW
	sewect CWYPTO_WIB_AES
	impwy CWYPTO_AES
	sewect CWYPTO_CMAC
	sewect CWYPTO_ECB
	sewect CWYPTO_SHA256
	sewect CWYPTO_ECDH
	hewp
	  Bwuetooth is wow-cost, wow-powew, showt-wange wiwewess technowogy.
	  It was designed as a wepwacement fow cabwes and othew showt-wange
	  technowogies wike IwDA.  Bwuetooth opewates in pewsonaw awea wange
	  that typicawwy extends up to 10 metews.  Mowe infowmation about
	  Bwuetooth can be found at <https://www.bwuetooth.com/>.

	  Winux Bwuetooth subsystem consist of sevewaw wayews:
	     Bwuetooth Cowe
		HCI device and connection managew, scheduwew
		SCO audio winks
		W2CAP (Wogicaw Wink Contwow and Adaptation Pwotocow)
		SMP (Secuwity Managew Pwotocow) on WE (Wow Enewgy) winks
		ISO isochwonous winks
	     HCI Device dwivews (Intewface to the hawdwawe)
	     WFCOMM Moduwe (WFCOMM Pwotocow)  
	     BNEP Moduwe (Bwuetooth Netwowk Encapsuwation Pwotocow)
	     CMTP Moduwe (CAPI Message Twanspowt Pwotocow)
	     HIDP Moduwe (Human Intewface Device Pwotocow)

	  Say Y hewe to compiwe Bwuetooth suppowt into the kewnew ow say M to
	  compiwe it as moduwe (bwuetooth).

	  To use Winux Bwuetooth subsystem, you wiww need sevewaw usew-space
	  utiwities wike hciconfig and bwuetoothd.  These utiwities and updates
	  to Bwuetooth kewnew moduwes awe pwovided in the BwueZ packages.  Fow
	  mowe infowmation, see <http://www.bwuez.owg/>.

